original_title: The Velvet Underground: Psychiatrist's Convention, NYC, 1966
overview: The Velvet Underground's first public appearance, filmed in Super 8 at a Psychiatrist's Convention, at the Delmonico Hotel, New York, January 14, 1966. Andy Warhol was invited to speak at the annual banquet of the New York Society for Clinical Psychiatry. He brought along the Velvets and other factory regulars.
title: The Velvet Underground: Psychiatrist's Convention, NYC, 1966
